data.description: Nestled within the charming community of Walnut Grove, this inviting four-bedroom two, two-bathroom ranch offers an ideal blend of comfort and style. Situated on a spacious quarter-acre lot offering ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation in the fenced rear yard. Upon entering, you will be welcomed by an inviting foyer, a large family room with soaring ceilings, and a cozy fireplace, perfect for gathering during chilly evenings. A dining room/sitting area flanks the family room, and a breakfast room overlooks the screened-in porch and kitchen with ample cabinet, counter space, and pantry. On the opposite side of the home is a fantastic owner's suite with a walk-in closet, soaker tub, shower, and large vanity with double sinks. Three additional good-sized bedrooms and a well-appointed bath complete the suite. Conveniently located, you'll enjoy easy access to interstates for seamless commuting and many shopping and dining options just moments away. Embrace the convenience of city living while relishing in the comfort of a close-knit neighborhood.
